00:00:06.986 --> 00:01:09.361 align:middle line:90%


00:01:09.361 --> 00:01:13.360 align:middle line:10%
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:18.320 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, I have found being on
this earth the most incredible

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:20.540 align:middle line:10%
adventure.

00:01:20.540 --> 00:01:27.360 align:middle line:84%
I've loved every minute of
it, and I often get curious

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:29.990 align:middle line:84%
that there's so
much complaint going

00:01:29.990 --> 00:01:32.720 align:middle line:90%
on when we're given so much.

00:01:32.720 --> 00:01:38.960 align:middle line:84%
That sounds la-di-dah, and so
on, but it's really the truth.

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:42.440 align:middle line:10%
So I write books
about it because I'm

00:01:42.440 --> 00:01:45.030 align:middle line:10%
trying to get certain
points across,

00:01:45.030 --> 00:01:49.080 align:middle line:10%
and I really didn't start
that until quite late--

00:01:49.080 --> 00:01:49.880 align:middle line:10%
book writing.

00:01:49.880 --> 00:01:52.400 align:middle line:10%


00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:59.940 align:middle line:10%
I had really a happy childhood,
and I was given free reign,

00:01:59.940 --> 00:02:01.740 align:middle line:10%
and I used to
spend a lot of time

00:02:01.740 --> 00:02:05.460 align:middle line:10%
up on a place called
Dorchester Hill.

00:02:05.460 --> 00:02:12.000 align:middle line:84%
And so I'm all by myself, and
I had a nice, nice childhood.

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:15.970 align:middle line:84%
But when I was seven,
they sent me to school,

00:02:15.970 --> 00:02:19.150 align:middle line:90%
said I had to go to school.

00:02:19.150 --> 00:02:23.020 align:middle line:84%
And the first day in
school was a nightmare

00:02:23.020 --> 00:02:27.350 align:middle line:84%
because the teacher punished the
boy in front of me-- not me--

00:02:27.350 --> 00:02:30.520 align:middle line:90%
but I was the teacher's pet.

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:34.830 align:middle line:84%
And a terrible thing
happened, I thought,

00:02:34.830 --> 00:02:36.410 align:middle line:84%
to the little boy
in front of me,

00:02:36.410 --> 00:02:39.500 align:middle line:84%
who pulled a little
girl's pigtails.

00:02:39.500 --> 00:02:43.400 align:middle line:84%
And the teacher did so
many awful things to him

00:02:43.400 --> 00:02:46.730 align:middle line:84%
and finally had gagged
him and struck him

00:02:46.730 --> 00:02:50.360 align:middle line:84%
in the knee hole
of her desk tied up

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:51.750 align:middle line:90%
for the rest of the day.

00:02:51.750 --> 00:02:56.060 align:middle line:84%
And I went home, and I said, I
will never go back there again.

00:02:56.060 --> 00:02:59.750 align:middle line:84%
And my older brother said,
if you don't go to school,

00:02:59.750 --> 00:03:02.090 align:middle line:90%
they'll put you in jail.

00:03:02.090 --> 00:03:05.720 align:middle line:84%
And this great rage
filled me, and I came out

00:03:05.720 --> 00:03:09.200 align:middle line:84%
with this statement--
but I own myself.

00:03:09.200 --> 00:03:11.750 align:middle line:90%
They don't own me.

00:03:11.750 --> 00:03:14.840 align:middle line:84%
So I proceeded to be
a very bad student.

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:18.710 align:middle line:84%
I skipped school constantly,
and I would actually

00:03:18.710 --> 00:03:22.310 align:middle line:84%
hide out in places where
they couldn't find me.

00:03:22.310 --> 00:03:25.550 align:middle line:84%
I've never quite forgotten
that and my protest

00:03:25.550 --> 00:03:29.890 align:middle line:84%
that I owned myself,
and I think that's been

00:03:29.890 --> 00:03:33.890 align:middle line:90%
one of the [INAUDIBLE].

00:03:33.890 --> 00:03:36.810 align:middle line:84%
And it's not a pretense
or anything else.

00:03:36.810 --> 00:03:41.830 align:middle line:84%
It's just the way it was
and has been all my life.

00:03:41.830 --> 00:03:44.430 align:middle line:90%


00:03:44.430 --> 00:03:47.820 align:middle line:10%
>> One of the most miserable
times of my life and his was

00:03:47.820 --> 00:03:50.300 align:middle line:10%
