00:04:49.640 --> 00:04:54.170 align:middle line:84%
And anything that gets in
the way of that slavish--

00:04:54.170 --> 00:04:58.850 align:middle line:84%
I mean, just this
real enslavement

00:04:58.850 --> 00:05:01.745 align:middle line:84%
by an economic
system, as we have.

00:05:01.745 --> 00:05:04.126 align:middle line:84%
