00:05:05.660 --> 00:05:08.460 align:middle line:90%


00:05:08.460 --> 00:05:13.290 align:middle line:10%
Rudolf Steiner-- I consider
one of the great geniuses

00:05:13.290 --> 00:05:15.960 align:middle line:10%
of the last six centuries.

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:20.160 align:middle line:84%
Steiner had it
really figured out.

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:25.230 align:middle line:10%
Waldorf education-- it's called
Waldorf because a tobacco

00:05:25.230 --> 00:05:29.610 align:middle line:10%
company asked Steiner,
would he set up

00:05:29.610 --> 00:05:33.420 align:middle line:10%
an education system for
the children of the workers

00:05:33.420 --> 00:05:35.320 align:middle line:10%
in the tobacco company?

00:05:35.320 --> 00:05:38.850 align:middle line:10%
There's something really
hilarious about that whole

00:05:38.850 --> 00:05:40.980 align:middle line:10%
back and forth.

00:05:40.980 --> 00:05:43.620 align:middle line:84%
And they wanted their
children to have something

00:05:43.620 --> 00:05:46.800 align:middle line:90%
better than they had had.

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:49.980 align:middle line:84%
And so Rudolf Steiner
came up with what we now

00:05:49.980 --> 00:05:54.150 align:middle line:90%
call Waldorf education.

00:05:54.150 --> 00:05:58.350 align:middle line:84%
And anyone who has ever really
gone into Waldorf education

00:05:58.350 --> 00:06:06.720 align:middle line:84%
sits back just simply amazed
at the incredible capacity

00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:10.050 align:middle line:84%
of the three or
four-year-old child

00:06:10.050 --> 00:06:13.250 align:middle line:84%
to move for their own
well-being at all times.

00:06:13.250 --> 00:06:16.950 align:middle line:10%
They're always moving
for their well-being.

00:06:16.950 --> 00:06:21.570 align:middle line:10%
And Steiner's Waldorf
school was where

00:06:21.570 --> 00:06:25.920 align:middle line:10%
that could be nurtured
fully and completely.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:31.260 align:middle line:10%
And if Waldorf
schools had really

00:06:31.260 --> 00:06:33.500 align:middle line:10%
spread over the whole world--

00:06:33.500 --> 00:06:38.820 align:middle line:10%
I'm serious-- I think it
changed just about everything.

00:06:38.820 --> 00:06:45.070 align:middle line:10%
In about 1920, when--

00:06:45.070 --> 00:06:49.410 align:middle line:10%
Steiner, I think, left in '23.

00:06:49.410 --> 00:06:54.990 align:middle line:10%
About that time,
the earliest Nazis

00:06:54.990 --> 00:07:00.820 align:middle line:10%
had begun to move as
a party in Germany.

00:07:00.820 --> 00:07:06.410 align:middle line:10%
And it's rumored-- someone
thinks that possibly they

00:07:06.410 --> 00:07:11.190 align:middle line:10%
poisoned Steiner because
he died very mysteriously--

00:07:11.190 --> 00:07:15.900 align:middle line:10%
because he was in the way.

00:07:15.900 --> 00:07:18.530 align:middle line:10%
And one of the first
things the Nazis did

00:07:18.530 --> 00:07:24.600 align:middle line:10%
when they took over Germany was
to seize all of the information

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:25.400 align:middle line:10%
centers--

00:07:25.400 --> 00:07:28.310 align:middle line:10%
radio, newspapers, and so on.

00:07:28.310 --> 00:07:32.540 align:middle line:84%
This is when the Nazis
took over fully--

00:07:32.540 --> 00:07:34.760 align:middle line:90%
the Hitler business.

00:07:34.760 --> 00:07:40.490 align:middle line:84%
But above all, they stopped all
Waldorf education in Germany,

00:07:40.490 --> 00:07:42.590 align:middle line:90%
and it was red-hot in Germany.

00:07:42.590 --> 00:07:45.980 align:middle line:84%
Everybody was trying to get
their child in a Waldorf

00:07:45.980 --> 00:07:47.750 align:middle line:90%
school.

00:07:47.750 --> 00:07:50.900 align:middle line:84%
And here, all of a sudden,
this newcomer, this Hitler

00:07:50.900 --> 00:07:53.000 align:middle line:90%
closes them all down.

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:57.230 align:middle line:84%
And they said, well, why did
you pick on Waldorf schools

00:07:57.230 --> 00:07:59.000 align:middle line:90%
and close them down?

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:01.850 align:middle line:84%
And he said because
I want children

00:08:01.850 --> 00:08:05.750 align:middle line:84%
trained from the
beginning to obey.

00:08:05.750 --> 00:08:07.985 align:middle line:90%
Waldorf teaches them to think.

00:08:07.985 --> 00:08:11.040 align:middle line:90%


00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:18.550 align:middle line:10%
And so there we have this
marvelously clear insight

00:08:18.550 --> 00:08:22.710 align:middle line:10%
into the two forces that are
still operating in the world

00:08:22.710 --> 00:08:26.120 align:middle line:10%
today as it was then.

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:32.150 align:middle line:84%
These are those
that want control

00:08:32.150 --> 00:08:34.429 align:middle line:84%
and to be the head
of the control,

00:08:34.429 --> 00:08:36.840 align:middle line:84%
the master of the
control, and those

00:08:36.840 --> 00:08:41.009 align:middle line:84%
who want the true unfolding
of human intelligence.

