00:33:00.890 --> 00:33:04.830 align:middle line:10%
proselyte or whatever,
get at other people--

00:33:04.830 --> 00:33:10.160 align:middle line:10%
oh, here, let me tell you, and
form an organization that's

00:33:10.160 --> 00:33:11.940 align:middle line:10%
going to change the world--

00:33:11.940 --> 00:33:13.560 align:middle line:10%
long gone.

00:33:13.560 --> 00:33:18.020 align:middle line:10%
You can never do anything
except one more interference

00:33:18.020 --> 00:33:22.350 align:middle line:10%
