00:33:22.350 --> 00:33:24.370 align:middle line:10%
And so we--

00:33:24.370 --> 00:33:26.865 align:middle line:10%
I dare say almost all--
except the Quakers.

00:33:26.865 --> 00:33:29.400 align:middle line:90%


