I make the exception
with the Quakers

00:33:32.840 --> 00:33:38.400 align:middle line:84%
because they've
escaped that danger.

00:33:38.400 --> 00:33:42.360 align:middle line:90%


00:33:42.360 --> 00:33:47.270 align:middle line:10%
I remember when I first
came across the work of one

00:33:47.270 --> 00:33:55.850 align:middle line:10%
of the early Quakers who never
made a move without checking

00:33:55.850 --> 00:33:58.910 align:middle line:10%
with his heart, without
checking internally,

00:33:58.910 --> 00:34:01.790 align:middle line:10%
should I or should
I not do that?

00:34:01.790 --> 00:34:07.660 align:middle line:10%
And he had developed it to a
real source of information,

00:34:07.660 --> 00:34:11.850 align:middle line:10%
even to the extent if
he were going along

00:34:11.850 --> 00:34:15.630 align:middle line:10%
and saw a division in
the road and wasn't sure

00:34:15.630 --> 00:34:17.940 align:middle line:10%
of which way to
go, he would always

00:34:17.940 --> 00:34:24.073 align:middle line:10%
stop and wait for his heart
to tell him which way to go.

00:34:24.073 --> 00:34:27.031 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:34:27.031 --> 00:34:38.370 align:middle line:90%


00:34:38.370 --> 00:34:46.280 align:middle line:10%
When I dropped out of the yoga
I had followed for 10 years--

00:34:46.280 --> 00:34:49.150 align:middle line:10%
and I loved it dearly--

00:34:49.150 --> 00:34:53.800 align:middle line:10%
I found that I couldn't
do that any more.

00:34:53.800 --> 00:34:56.340 align:middle line:10%


00:34:56.340 --> 00:34:59.720 align:middle line:10%
It was-- that had just
closed its door to me.

00:34:59.720 --> 00:35:04.320 align:middle line:10%
Now, remember that afternoon
when I took the slogan--

00:35:04.320 --> 00:35:06.440 align:middle line:10%
I've forgotten what it was--

00:35:06.440 --> 00:35:10.010 align:middle line:10%
that we said to ourselves
to calm our mind down

00:35:10.010 --> 00:35:17.470 align:middle line:10%
and immersed myself in it,
wondering what am I to do now?

00:35:17.470 --> 00:35:21.000 align:middle line:10%
Because I had followed
this thing for 10 years.

00:35:21.000 --> 00:35:21.800 align:middle line:10%
It was a path.

00:35:21.800 --> 00:35:23.020 align:middle line:90%
It was a--

00:35:23.020 --> 00:35:25.860 align:middle line:84%
I had loads of
company on that path.

00:35:25.860 --> 00:35:29.490 align:middle line:84%
I lived it, and all sorts
of unordinary things

00:35:29.490 --> 00:35:31.890 align:middle line:90%
happened as a result of it.

00:35:31.890 --> 00:35:34.090 align:middle line:90%
What was I to do now?

00:35:34.090 --> 00:35:41.550 align:middle line:10%
And I simply waited
with that one thing--

00:35:41.550 --> 00:35:45.390 align:middle line:10%
what to do now?

00:35:45.390 --> 00:35:51.640 align:middle line:10%
And I got my
answer, and it came.

00:35:51.640 --> 00:35:54.530 align:middle line:10%
And I thought about
it for a long time.

00:35:54.530 --> 00:35:57.650 align:middle line:10%
I heard it from my heart.

00:35:57.650 --> 00:36:02.150 align:middle line:10%
It was as though my heart had
spoken it very clearly to me,

00:36:02.150 --> 00:36:05.780 align:middle line:10%
and I did exactly
what it told me to do.

00:36:05.780 --> 00:36:13.640 align:middle line:10%
And we had an experience in yoga
of what this is the Blue Pearl.

00:36:13.640 --> 00:36:19.190 align:middle line:10%
And if you concentrate
on this Blue Pearl,

00:36:19.190 --> 00:36:21.325 align:middle line:10%
it takes you into
levels of consciousness

00:36:21.325 --> 00:36:23.930 align:middle line:10%
that are not ordinary.

00:36:23.930 --> 00:36:26.930 align:middle line:10%
And if things are going
well, occasionally you'll

00:36:26.930 --> 00:36:29.840 align:middle line:10%
see this little blue pearl.

00:36:29.840 --> 00:36:33.500 align:middle line:10%
Quite right-- that's
exactly what happened.

00:36:33.500 --> 00:36:37.460 align:middle line:10%
If you're in a group of people
who are practicing this from--

00:36:37.460 --> 00:36:39.980 align:middle line:10%
I think we were generally
up about a quarter of 3:00

00:36:39.980 --> 00:36:43.670 align:middle line:10%
in the morning to be
over at the shrine

00:36:43.670 --> 00:36:46.520 align:middle line:10%
where we did our
best meditating,

00:36:46.520 --> 00:36:48.650 align:middle line:10%
and you meditate
on this, and you've

00:36:48.650 --> 00:36:53.570 align:middle line:10%
been doing this for years, it
begins to pack a lot of energy.

00:36:53.570 --> 00:36:56.330 align:middle line:10%
And so this business
of the Blue Pearl

00:36:56.330 --> 00:37:00.730 align:middle line:10%
became absolutely
the utmost important.

00:37:00.730 --> 00:37:04.885 align:middle line:10%
And I was waiting when all
of a sudden, and this--

00:37:04.885 --> 00:37:06.830 align:middle line:10%
I'll skip all the
leading up to it--

00:37:06.830 --> 00:37:12.230 align:middle line:10%
when I knew that I had
to leave this yoga,

00:37:12.230 --> 00:37:14.285 align:middle line:10%
I had to leave
Siddah Yoga that I

00:37:14.285 --> 00:37:18.170 align:middle line:10%
had been happy in for 10 years.

00:37:18.170 --> 00:37:22.740 align:middle line:10%
And you know, it was
like leaving your mother

00:37:22.740 --> 00:37:24.010 align:middle line:10%
or something.

00:37:24.010 --> 00:37:27.200 align:middle line:10%
It was kind of a puzzling thing.

00:37:27.200 --> 00:37:29.180 align:middle line:10%
What then?

00:37:29.180 --> 00:37:38.920 align:middle line:10%
And this voice came
and came from my heart.

00:37:38.920 --> 00:37:44.820 align:middle line:10%
I heard for the first time
in my life, an actual heart--

00:37:44.820 --> 00:37:50.920 align:middle line:10%
I mean, an actual voice from my
heart, directly from my heart.

00:37:50.920 --> 00:37:58.630 align:middle line:10%
And it was a tremendous
experience from me.

00:37:58.630 --> 00:38:04.090 align:middle line:10%
And this will sound
awfully la-di-dah,

00:38:04.090 --> 00:38:06.580 align:middle line:10%
but to me, in that
particular state,

00:38:06.580 --> 00:38:09.400 align:middle line:10%
it was the voice of Jesus.

00:38:09.400 --> 00:38:12.490 align:middle line:10%
And I had never been
a Jesus fanatic,

00:38:12.490 --> 00:38:17.410 align:middle line:10%
but it was the voice of Jesus
telling me exactly what to do.

00:38:17.410 --> 00:38:21.160 align:middle line:84%
And I turned around, and I
did exactly what it said.

00:38:21.160 --> 00:38:25.560 align:middle line:84%
And for about a half
hour, this great shower

00:38:25.560 --> 00:38:29.680 align:middle line:84%
of these little blue pearls
seemed to fall all around me.

00:38:29.680 --> 00:38:34.230 align:middle line:84%
And I went into this
remarkable state of bliss.

00:38:34.230 --> 00:38:37.570 align:middle line:10%
And what all that
leads to is too long.

00:38:37.570 --> 00:38:44.920 align:middle line:10%
But it's typical of,
again, these capacities

00:38:44.920 --> 00:38:51.370 align:middle line:10%
we have within us that are not
in keeping with our culture.

00:38:51.370 --> 00:38:55.730 align:middle line:10%
And if you act outside our
culture, what are you called?

00:38:55.730 --> 00:39:01.180 align:middle line:10%
A cult, belonging to a cult.
But when all you're doing

00:39:01.180 --> 00:39:05.670 align:middle line:10%
is really following your heart.

00:39:05.670 --> 00:39:09.970 align:middle line:84%
>> You know, Jesus's
conversation with his disciples

00:39:09.970 --> 00:39:10.770 align:middle line:90%
is just--

00:39:10.770 --> 00:39:12.270 align:middle line:90%
and the Sermon on the Mount--

00:39:12.270 --> 00:39:16.200 align:middle line:84%
are just the essence
of older cultures.

00:39:16.200 --> 00:39:19.770 align:middle line:84%
You know, in Matthew 25,
the disciples come to Jesus,

00:39:19.770 --> 00:39:23.108 align:middle line:84%
and they say, how
do we get to heaven?

00:39:23.108 --> 00:39:25.650 align:middle line:84%
You know, we're all-- you know,
you're going to go to heaven.

00:39:25.650 --> 00:39:26.692 align:middle line:90%
We'd like to go with you.

00:39:26.692 --> 00:39:28.260 align:middle line:84%
And we want to
hang out with you.

00:39:28.260 --> 00:39:30.180 align:middle line:84%
And he said, oh, it's
very straightforward.

00:39:30.180 --> 00:39:33.420 align:middle line:84%
You know, in the end of days,
I'll be sitting here judging,

00:39:33.420 --> 00:39:35.150 align:middle line:84%
separating the sheep
from the goats.

00:39:35.150 --> 00:39:36.900 align:middle line:84%
And the sheep are going
to heaven with me,

00:39:36.900 --> 00:39:40.170 align:middle line:90%
and the goats are going to hell.

00:39:40.170 --> 00:39:43.180 align:middle line:84%
And I will say to the sheep,
you know, when I was thirsty,

00:39:43.180 --> 00:39:43.980 align:middle line:90%
you gave me water.

00:39:43.980 --> 00:39:45.210 align:middle line:84%
When I was hungry,
you gave me food.

00:39:45.210 --> 00:39:46.770 align:middle line:84%
When I was in prison,
you came and visited me.

00:39:46.770 --> 00:39:48.060 align:middle line:90%
When I was sick, you healed me.

00:39:48.060 --> 00:39:49.435 align:middle line:84%
When I was naked,
you clothed me.

00:39:49.435 --> 00:39:51.330 align:middle line:90%
When I was in jail--

00:39:51.330 --> 00:39:53.100 align:middle line:84%
I think I said
that-- visited me.

00:39:53.100 --> 00:39:55.320 align:middle line:84%
Basically, and I went
with through the list.

00:39:55.320 --> 00:39:57.990 align:middle line:84%
And then he said, and
I'll say to the goats,

00:39:57.990 --> 00:40:01.380 align:middle line:84%
you didn't do those
things, so off you go.

00:40:01.380 --> 00:40:03.030 align:middle line:90%
And at that point--

00:40:03.030 --> 00:40:04.500 align:middle line:84%
you know, this seems like a
good story up to that point.

00:40:04.500 --> 00:40:06.000 align:middle line:84%
At that point,
though, the disciples

00:40:06.000 --> 00:40:08.850 align:middle line:84%
freak out because they've
never seen him hungry.

00:40:08.850 --> 00:40:10.350 align:middle line:90%
They've never seen him thirsty.

00:40:10.350 --> 00:40:11.820 align:middle line:84%
They've never seen
him in prison.

00:40:11.820 --> 00:40:13.110 align:middle line:90%
They've never seen him naked.

00:40:13.110 --> 00:40:15.450 align:middle line:84%
So you know, homeless,
or clothesless.

00:40:15.450 --> 00:40:17.407 align:middle line:84%
And so they say to him,
oh my God, you know,

00:40:17.407 --> 00:40:18.990 align:middle line:84%
we've never seen
you-- you know, we've

00:40:18.990 --> 00:40:20.580 align:middle line:84%
never been able to do
these things for you.

00:40:20.580 --> 00:40:22.163 align:middle line:84%
How are we going to
make it to heaven?

00:40:22.163 --> 00:40:23.160 align:middle line:90%
We're screwed.

00:40:23.160 --> 00:40:26.850 align:middle line:84%
And he said, as you do
it to the least among us,

00:40:26.850 --> 00:40:29.250 align:middle line:90%
you've done it to me.

00:40:29.250 --> 00:40:33.798 align:middle line:84%
And that's the essential
message of an ancient culture.

00:40:33.798 --> 00:40:35.340 align:middle line:84%
You know, in the
Sermon on the Mount,

00:40:35.340 --> 00:40:39.150 align:middle line:84%
he talked about the
least shall be first.

00:40:39.150 --> 00:40:41.970 align:middle line:84%
That's the essential message
of the ancient cultures.

00:40:41.970 --> 00:40:43.500 align:middle line:84%
And that's the
message that we need

00:40:43.500 --> 00:40:45.630 align:middle line:84%
to be integrating
into our culture,

00:40:45.630 --> 00:40:50.190 align:middle line:84%
and there's 100,000 churches
probably within 1,000 miles

00:40:50.190 --> 00:40:53.850 align:middle line:84%
of us that are preaching
Jesus right now

00:40:53.850 --> 00:40:56.910 align:middle line:84%
and don't understand that
core message because it's been

00:40:56.910 --> 00:40:58.920 align:middle line:90%
so polluted by our culture.

00:40:58.920 --> 00:41:01.470 align:middle line:90%


00:41:01.470 --> 00:41:08.370 align:middle line:84%
>> Joe was really important
for me in 1996 when I left this

00:41:08.370 --> 00:41:12.780 align:middle line:84%
church and, in many ways,
left ministry for a while.

00:41:12.780 --> 00:41:15.930 align:middle line:84%
It was a period in my
life from which I really

00:41:15.930 --> 00:41:19.050 align:middle line:84%
had to seek some
kind of guidance

00:41:19.050 --> 00:41:22.890 align:middle line:84%
that I couldn't get in a
religious setting anymore.

00:41:22.890 --> 00:41:27.630 align:middle line:84%
Everything comes from this
spontaneous experience

00:41:27.630 --> 00:41:32.250 align:middle line:84%
of transmission
that was his life.

00:41:32.250 --> 00:41:34.200 align:middle line:84%
