00:43:31.850 --> 00:43:34.640 align:middle line:84%
is really how we
understand Darwinism now,

00:43:34.640 --> 00:43:38.370 align:middle line:84%
and which is a complete
misunderstanding, frankly,

00:43:38.370 --> 00:43:40.220 align:middle line:90%
of much of what Darwin wrote.

00:43:40.220 --> 00:43:42.925 align:middle line:84%
