level of our schools,

00:43:44.550 --> 00:43:47.420 align:middle line:84%
where we're pitting our
children against each other

00:43:47.420 --> 00:43:50.600 align:middle line:84%
in this competitive way and
making some feel like failures

00:43:50.600 --> 00:43:53.750 align:middle line:84%
and making others feel like,
you know, little Donald Trumps--

00:43:53.750 --> 00:43:58.510 align:middle line:84%
you know, little kings,
little emperor kings.

00:43:58.510 --> 00:44:02.100 align:middle line:84%
And then that dysfunction then
echoes through their lives

00:44:02.100 --> 00:44:04.550 align:middle line:84%
and echoes through our
culture, and it just

00:44:04.550 --> 00:44:06.260 align:middle line:90%
continues on and on.

00:44:06.260 --> 00:44:10.200 align:middle line:84%
