00:44:35.600 --> 00:44:37.580 align:middle line:84%
That's what we're
teaching our society.

00:44:37.580 --> 00:44:39.440 align:middle line:84%
That's the basis
of our culture--

00:44:39.440 --> 00:44:41.450 align:middle line:90%
cancer.

00:44:41.450 --> 00:44:47.020 align:middle line:84%
